at my trial.

1158
01:10:41,445 --> 01:10:42,989
You believe that at least?

1159
01:10:44,323 --> 01:10:45,867
I believe you told us the facts,

1160
01:10:45,909 --> 01:10:47,994
but the truth is something else.

1161
01:10:52,957 --> 01:10:54,751
I went back...

