1392
01:25:56,819 --> 01:26:00,948
<i>♪ Give it all away... ♪</i>

1393
01:26:04,493 --> 01:26:07,329
Okay.

1394
01:26:08,998 --> 01:26:11,166
Good boy. Sit.

1395
